sub_title: Mechanical engineer with great expertise in mechanical design and CAD-CAE-CAM software, proficient in FEM-FVM simulation, and GD&T analysis, with knowledge in heat transfer, fluid dynamics, and materials resistance
summary: Mag. in engineering and innovation management from Universidad Catolica de Colombia, Mag. in engineering and innovation management from Università Degli Studi Di Salerno, Salerno, Italy with a bachelor degree in Mechanical engineering with great expertise in projects management, mechanical design, 3D CAD-CAM-CAE, GD&T analysis, FEM and FVM simulations, thermodynamics and, heat transfer phenomena applied to industrial equipment. Also experience in Artificial intelligence, programing with Matlab and Python.
